{"tid":1642055,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"英二戰軍官靈柩蓋上中華民國國旗","createTime":"2019-10-09T14:25:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-10T05:28:05.000Z","uid":48390,"like":28,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"18bba726961b934a878915ab4b7b70c507ae1557","tid":1642055,"uid":48390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T14:25:50.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/2018/09/18/british-veterans-coffin-draped-taiwanese-flag-honouring-chinese/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.telegraph.co.uk%2Fnews%2F2018%2F09%2F18%2Fbritish-veterans-coffin-draped-taiwanese-flag-honouring-chinese%2F&d=FZDcFY5BXo0CBgddFpFX54v2J6e4EmGiVIqwvzORC%2Fw%3D&h=277669d6\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/2018/09/18/british-veterans-coffin-draped-taiwanese-flag-honouring-chinese/</a><br />\n<br />\n二戰老軍官Fitzpatrick上尉戰時被派遣到緬甸作戰，唯所屬部隊被萬餘日軍圍於仁安羌<br />\n<br />\n最後我國民革命軍入緬遠征軍第113團800餘人於團長劉放吾上校帶領下，傾力營救出被圍英軍7000餘人<br />\n<br />\nFitzpatrick上尉被救出後，畢生對中華民國與及國軍心懷感念之情，曾親筆著有兩本書，以對英國國內宣揚我國在二次大戰中之貢獻<br />\n<br />\nFitzpatrick年老時曾再一次到訪我國，並揚言希望死後可以蓋上我中華民國國旗，以作其人生中對國軍將士最後之致敬<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TvinJXP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTvinJXP.jpg&h=d3653f61&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CRUmZwa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCRUmZwa.jpg&h=189d0a53&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6WC0vCT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6WC0vCT.jpg&h=d0e093ce&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8b95e0763b9da49de09b94b39af86345940ab3d0","tid":1642055,"uid":56428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T14:29:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e40da7e9b97e5b0ce2ea8459e99699cbbd95be46","tid":1642055,"uid":4